# Examples:
# If you have multiple teams, you can specify different owners for different areas:
# /frontend/ @frontend-team
# /backend/ @backend-team
# /mobile/ @mobile-team

# You can also use email addresses instead of usernames:
# docs/ user@example.com

# For more complex rules, you can use patterns:
# *.config.js @config-team
# src/components/** @ui-team
# src/utils/** @utils-team

# Optional reviewers (not required, but suggested)
# These will be added as reviewers but won't block the PR
# docs/ @documentation-team

# Emergency contacts for critical files
# If you need immediate attention for security issues
# SECURITY.md @security-team @emergency-contact